パッケージ xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator.trigger

クラス SleptInBedTrigger

java.lang.Object
xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator.trigger.Trigger
xyz.mlserver.advancementcreator.trigger.SleptInBedTrigger
public class SleptInBedTrigger extends Trigger
Fires when the player successfully enters a bed (the player does not have to pass the night). For example if the bed explodes, such as from trying to sleep in the nether, this trigger will not fire.
